thread.title: Royce
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by Royce

author: Royce
title: Royce
text:
Was a nice hire vehicle to drive, need a bit more attention to detail with the cleanliness of the car tho mud spots and bug splats on the front bumper.
When we got to Newcastle airport we went straight to the desk the lady that serviced me lacked customer service no smile and was a bit demanding.
But nevertheless the car the price was reasonable
